21:27.861 --> 21:29.863
What's the matter, Jeremiah?

21:31.998 --> 21:33.767
Are you all right?

21:35.000 --> 21:36.636
No.

21:37.836 --> 21:39.940
I'm not all right.

21:42.642 --> 21:44.210
Did I do something wrong?

21:49.583 --> 21:50.651
Wrong?

21:54.587 --> 21:57.123
Everything you do is wrong.

21:59.726 --> 22:01.594
I'm so sorry, Jeremiah.

22:05.765 --> 22:10.767
Is there anything I can do
to make you feel better?

22:10.769 --> 22:14.541
There is nothing you can do.

22:18.612 --> 22:20.113
It's her.

22:21.948 --> 22:25.382
I feel naked without her.

22:25.384 --> 22:27.054
Naked.

22:31.157 --> 22:32.560
Do you hear me?

22:33.759 --> 22:36.226
I-I...

22:36.228 --> 22:38.729
I said, "Do you hear me?"

22:38.731 --> 22:40.665
Yes, Jeremiah.
I hear you.

22:40.667 --> 22:42.800
"Yes, Jeremiah.

22:42.802 --> 22:45.736
I hear you."
Really?

22:45.738 --> 22:50.944
Because, sometimes, I don't
think you hear anything at all.

22:52.812 --> 22:56.350
And I am truly
worried about that.

22:57.283 --> 23:02.957
If you are not with me,
you will not ascend.

23:05.057 --> 23:11.396
- MARLENE: Jeremiah, I...
- Please...

23:11.398 --> 23:17.067
just be quiet
and go fetch me Brother Swan.

23:17.069 --> 23:18.835
Okay.

23:18.837 --> 23:23.911
I said,
"Go fetch me Brother Swan."

23:46.766 --> 23:48.334
There you are.

23:51.103 --> 23:53.740
What can I do for you, Jeremiah?

23:55.174 --> 23:58.842
I need you to get me
that girl I saw.

23:58.844 --> 24:00.381
I need her.

24:02.347 --> 24:04.148
I need her now.

24:04.150 --> 24:09.055
Jeremiah, consider it done.

24:13.293 --> 24:15.796
Do you have the Horn of Abraxas?

24:46.359 --> 24:48.762
Do you know what to do?

24:49.328 --> 24:50.863
I do.

24:53.098 --> 24:54.098
Hey.

24:56.102 --> 24:58.906
Why don't we offer up
the porker, too?

25:00.440 --> 25:02.974
Just to seal the deal.

25:02.976 --> 25:05.379
That is such a good idea.

25:07.279 --> 25:12.719
That lard-ass, he couldn't
find his nose in a mirror.

25:13.385 --> 25:15.455
[LAUGHS]

25:27.232 --> 25:29.368
I knew I could count on you.

25:32.838 --> 25:36.442
I can always count on you.

25:37.811 --> 25:38.811
Buddy.

25:41.180 --> 25:43.880
Oh, thank you, Jeremiah.

25:43.882 --> 25:45.219
Thank you.

25:49.354 --> 25:51.024
Before you go...

25:53.125 --> 25:55.161
...send in Sister Lucy.

26:00.333 --> 26:02.436
BROTHER SWAN:
Of course.

26:37.603 --> 26:39.840
[FOOTSTEPS APPROACH]

26:41.341 --> 26:43.243
