That's a cool T-shirt.

26:47.980 --> 26:49.546
Oh, thanks.

26:49.548 --> 26:51.916
What you reading?

26:51.918 --> 26:53.551
MANDY:
A novel.

26:53.553 --> 26:54.854
Oh.

26:56.055 --> 26:57.356
How do you like it?

26:59.158 --> 27:01.594
Yeah, I think it's
Lenora Tor's best book.

27:04.998 --> 27:06.033
Hmm.

27:08.167 --> 27:09.667
I guess you live around here.

27:09.669 --> 27:13.974
Yeah. We live just down
near Crystal Lake.

27:15.507 --> 27:17.443
Oh, that sounds lovely.

27:21.613 --> 27:23.514
It's 5 bucks.

27:23.516 --> 27:24.852
Oh, yeah.

27:39.065 --> 27:40.433
Well...

27:47.306 --> 27:48.976
See you later.

27:50.176 --> 27:52.379
