33:54.306 --> 33:55.808
[GULPING]

34:06.484 --> 34:10.422
Blood for blood.

34:14.460 --> 34:17.330
More.

34:27.005 --> 34:28.942
First things first.

34:30.909 --> 34:31.875
<i>Aah!</i>

