[GASPING]

37:19.143 --> 37:21.180
[ELECTRICITY BUZZING]

37:36.661 --> 37:37.897
[GRUNTS]

38:16.035 --> 38:17.536
MARLENE:
Don't worry.

38:20.105 --> 38:22.575
Those scary men are gone now.

38:24.243 --> 38:28.014
They got what they came for,
and they're gone.

38:33.618 --> 38:35.921
I guess you're wondering
where your hubby is.

38:37.989 --> 38:40.158
Don't you worry.
He's just fine.

38:42.227 --> 38:46.763
And he'll stay that way
as long as you're a good girl

38:46.765 --> 38:48.600
and do as you're told.

38:56.107 --> 38:57.843
- [SLAP]
- [MUFFLED GROAN]

38:59.877 --> 39:01.580
MARLENE:
Do you understand me?

39:03.147 --> 39:06.750
You know, he thinks
you're so special,

39:06.752 --> 39:09.719
