what that means.

39:09.721 --> 39:12.792
The responsibility
is on you, buster.

39:27.006 --> 39:28.641
[GROANS]

39:29.875 --> 39:31.641
[MOANING]

39:31.643 --> 39:32.775
MARLENE: Open.

39:32.777 --> 39:34.747
[MANDY GROANING]

39:38.082 --> 39:39.251
MARLENE:
Very good.

39:42.087 --> 39:43.289
Very good.

39:59.805 --> 40:01.674
Hold still.

40:03.042 --> 40:04.277
Hold still.

40:08.814 --> 40:10.882
[MANDY GROANING]

40:12.151 --> 40:14.152
[MUFFLED SCREAMING]

40:17.156 --> 40:19.625
[MOANING]

40:21.727 --> 40:26.132
I like to call that
the cherry on top.

40:31.136 --> 40:33.672
It's all but a beautiful dream.

40:36.040 --> 40:38.377
A dream he's having right now.

40:43.047 --> 40:45.283
Won't you join us in that dream?

42:09.301 --> 42:15.842
I'm sorry for all
this fuss and muss.

42:17.942 --> 42:23.115
But when I saw you
on the road the other day...

42:26.919 --> 42:28.921
...you called out to me...

42:30.888 --> 42:32.892
...silently.

42:35.493 --> 42:36.995
And I listened.

42:41.834 --> 42:43.201
Look at me.

42:45.337 --> 42:47.039
[ECHOING]
Look at me!

42:49.507 --> 42:50.977
Tell me.

42:52.511 --> 42:54.247
What do you see?

43:04.288 --> 43:07.426
I see the reaper
fast approaching.

43:11.997 --> 43:14.163
Well, I recognized you,

43:14.165 --> 43:18.571
so I think in time...

43:20.172 --> 43:22.408
...you will recognize me.

43:25.243 --> 43:27.243
You know,

43:27.245 --> 43:31.348
all he wants is for his children

43:31.350 --> 43:34.319
to love one another.

43:39.190 --> 43:45.395
Now, I find that he allows me

43:45.397 --> 43:52.034
to express that love
in many ways,

43:52.036 --> 43:56.475
but one of those ways...

43:57.910 --> 43:59.478
...is music.

44:03.214 --> 44:05.183
Do you like the Carpenters?

44:06.384 --> 44:10.920
I think that
they're sensational,

44:10.922 --> 44:16.062
but this is even better.

44:17.129 --> 44:19.295
[CRACKLING]

44:19.297 --> 44:21.366
<i>[MID-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS]</i>

44:34.478 --> 44:36.147
What do you think?

44:38.582 --> 44:40.083
[MOANS]

44:40.085 --> 44:41.921
Shh. Shh. Wait.

44:43.254 --> 44:45.257
It's about to start.

44:52.663 --> 44:58.067
<i>♪ Every seed
that gives us life ♪</i>

44:58.069 --> 45:03.339
<i>♪ Every man must take a wife ♪</i>

45:03.341 --> 45:08.545
<i>♪ Only one sun ever shines ♪</i>

45:08.547 --> 45:12.551
<i>♪ Only one sun, yours and mine ♪</i>

45:13.685 --> 45:19.221
<i>♪ Jeremiah Sand was a righteous
man whose heart... ♪</i>

45:19.223 --> 45:21.357
You know, I was ready
to stand tall

45:21.359 --> 45:23.659
with the great,
grand glittery ones,

45:23.661 --> 45:26.161
but those scumbags
couldn't recognize

45:26.163 --> 45:27.998
a golden, radiant light

45:28.000 --> 45:31.036
even as it was cast
right down upon them.

45:32.004 --> 45:33.339
But thankfully...

45:35.006 --> 45:39.477
Thankfully,
he showed me another path.

45:40.779 --> 45:45.448
The path I have always
been truly destined for,

45:45.450 --> 45:52.621
something far greater
than mere fame or fortune.

45:52.623 --> 45:55.424
<i>♪ ...lessons well ♪</i>

45:55.426 --> 45:57.761
<i>♪ The light shines
through everything ♪</i>

45:57.763 --> 46:00.562
<i>♪ The light is true,
the lessons learned ♪</i>

46:00.564 --> 46:03.702
<i>♪ His song of you and me ♪</i>

46:11.209 --> 46:13.678
When I was at the bottom
of the pit...

46:15.480 --> 46:18.084
...screaming in the darkness...

46:19.518 --> 46:23.022
...racked with
unspeakable pain...

46:24.256 --> 46:28.094
...for having been denied
all that was rightfully mine...

46:32.464 --> 46:35.034
...he graced me with his light.

46:37.468 --> 46:42.575
His hot loving light.

46:45.477 --> 46:50.315
It flowed over me like
the pulse of a timeless wave.

46:52.651 --> 46:56.187
A wave of pure heat.

46:58.489 --> 47:05.797
A mainline of pure
and total acceptance.

47:10.669 --> 47:12.437
And he talked to me.

47:15.406 --> 47:17.475
Addressed me as a friend.

47:19.844 --> 47:25.683
He said, "Jeremiah,
they were wrong.

47:28.219 --> 47:31.056
And you are right.

47:33.257 --> 47:35.694
So right."

47:37.828 --> 47:41.132
And he blessed me
with his holy kiss.

47:44.201 --> 47:50.176
He said, "You are not separate
from all that is.

47:51.276 --> 47:53.745
So all that is...

47:55.312 --> 47:56.848
...is yours."

47:58.884 --> 48:02.784
And he gave me his deepest
and warmest permission

48:02.786 --> 48:05.455
to go out into this world

48:05.457 --> 48:10.096
and take what is
so very much mine.

48:12.696 --> 48:14.797
All of it.

48:14.799 --> 48:16.134
Mine.

48:17.301 --> 48:19.402
